            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I went through the documentation (more carefully this time), read some help pages, and looked at some issues, but I did not find any command that gives the output we want. I also sent a message on their discord, so if there is a way to do it, we'll probably find out.\r\n\r\n`bun pm ls -g` does show the path, but the output is not clear. It would be necessary to apply some filtering/parsing to get the right information. Even though that works, any change to the output would most likely just break the thing. This gives us two 'unstable' options (hardcoded and filtered output). We could go with one of them or just not merge this at all, at least for the moment.\r\n\r\nI should have gone through this before making the PR. My bad.",
