            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I guess we could just check the ones that returns faster first (just like that comment says). I could run some benchmarks (with hyperfine) to get the priority order. We could also just check by popularity. If the user probably has npm installed doesn't make much sense check for the others.\r\n\r\nThe yarn stuff can also early return, we might want to do something about that.",
